<s> Is there a comparison/equality operation in XQuery that allows me to decide if two strings are equal?  </s>
<s> Just to be clear, by "equal" I mean here really equal, i.e., without collation or anything like that.  </s>
<s> -- Jan Hidders  </s>
<s> You can use fn:compare using the Unicode codepoint collation.  </s>
<s> This will give you a "character by character" comparison.  </s>
<s> All the best, Ashok [mailto:public-qt-comments-request@w3.org]  </s>
